OL,3,CPlymouth set for referendum over
OL,4,Cwhether to have a 'directly elected
OL,5,Cmayor'
OL,7,FThe referendum is estimated to cost
OL,8,Fmore than #400,000.
OL,10,FAngus Forbes, former banker and
OL,11,Fhusband of ex-Strictly Come Dancing
OL,12,Fjudge Darcey Bussell, is leading the
OL,13,Fcampaign in favour of a mayor.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the 'Yes Plymouth
OL,16,FDEM' campaign said: "There is a clear
OL,17,Fappetite for change in our city.
OL,18,FPeople have seen the positive impact
OL,19,Fmayors have made on other cities in
OL,20,Fthe UK and abroad.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
