OL,3,CPlymouth set for referendum over
OL,4,Cwhether to have a 'directly elected
OL,5,Cmayor'
OL,7,F"The referendum is a chance for people
OL,8,Fto change their governance structure,
OL,9,Fand get a leader they really believe
OL,10,Fin, because they have voted them in
OL,11,Fdirectly.
OL,13,F"They can vote to break free from the
OL,14,Funsuccessful over-politicised
OL,15,Fcouncillor led model and change to
OL,16,Fhaving a mayor who is elected by
OL,17,Fvoters, someone who is able to unify
OL,18,Fand transform our city."
