OL,7,F"The campaign is built on
OL,8,Fmisinformation and false promises.
OL,9,FThey haven't been honest about what
OL,10,Fservices they would cut to pay for
OL,11,Fthis or why they're pushing a model
OL,12,Fthat's already failed elsewhere.
OL,14,F"This is a disastrous distraction from
OL,15,Fthe real issues facing our city.
OL,16,FPlymouth deserves better than being
OL,17,Fdragged into an expensive, pointless
OL,18,Fexperiment."
